reviews.review_text: good stuff I'll have whatever they were smoking, please.
Smoking Show! They sound so in sync and loose. Granted 73 is known for this type of play. But this show is exceptional. Thank you for this upload

So Good You'll Play it Again and Again Very exploratory and expressive. An unbelievably hot show--really, from beginning to end. Fantastically crystal clear, well-balanced recording. If Mom was alive I'd write home about it. This is the Grateful Dead the way you like to hear them--in all their glory. Wish there were more than five stars.
